1. *Taj* automobil je veoma skup. (That car is very expensive.)
2. Tačno je da *taj* događaj nije bio planiran. (It is true that this event was not planned.)
3. Ona je znala da će *taj* problem biti težak. (She knew that this problem would be difficult.)
4. *Taj* uspeh je bio dovoljan da nastavi dalje. (This success was enough to continue.)
5. Oni su se nadali da će *taj* projekat biti završen. (They hoped that this project would be finished.)